{"tid":705162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港一日經濟唔冧 都唔使惗獨立","createTime":"2018-06-17T02:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T03:56:29.000Z","uid":41389,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"84169fefbbc11f4c841519881a194c571e20d76c","tid":705162,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"基本上個個見錢開眼淪為共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢就自己移民走佬算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日可以打工養妻活兒安安穩穩人都唔會出黎反抗<br />\n而經常革命需要既低下階層亦都比政府啲雙三糧氹得開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經濟唔冧既話唔好話一半香港人<br />\n連10%都唔知團唔團結到<br />\n其實個個都有心想搞大佢 <br />\n係網上做鍵盤戰士抒發情緒<br />\n但無人願意係而家一個咁安穩既經濟體系入面放棄眼前既利益 而冒住比共慘黨清算又反抗力量薄弱既時候 行出黎<br />\n如果時機成熟 一支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲1999 sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153ff5c70401be98f6a255dc05d949770018e017","tid":705162,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e49b2df2a01fc4ea199a9f876e7555913c57eb0","tid":705162,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f6bb15f3ec4d21b43720e4d9f0c1aacb21f86f","tid":705162,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155159df2f0c75ac